WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.466 --> 00:00:02.366
Can my engagement to the Lu family continue?

2
00:00:03.133 --> 00:00:06.433
Qi Chan, you clearly said that you are responsible for me

3
00:00:06.466 --> 00:00:08.166
I said I was responsible for you.

4
00:00:08.266 --> 00:00:10.466
But it wasn't you who was at the hotel that night

5
00:00:10.466 --> 00:00:11.566
But the abyss

6
00:00:13.266 --> 00:00:14.800
How do you know that?

7
00:00:17.066 --> 00:00:18.033
Yes

8
00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:19.900
You said it.

9
00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:22.666
I'm not the one doing these things.

10
00:00:22.666 --> 00:00:24.233
You should ask Chen Yuanan.

11
00:00:24.366 --> 00:00:26.500
He sent our photos

12
00:00:26.533 --> 00:00:28.266
He's lying there in the hospital.

13
00:00:28.266 --> 00:00:30.000
I can't send any photos at all.

14
00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:33.400
Since you want to rob me of everything

15
00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:35.666
Then I can't let you get your wish.

16
00:00:41.133 --> 00:00:42.700
You still don't know your mistake

17
00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:44.200
Don't force me to do it

18
00:00:53.266 --> 00:00:54.066
And so forth.

19
00:00:54.966 --> 00:00:56.266
Something.

20
00:00:56.266 --> 00:00:58.633
We really should make a break between us

